            </h1>
            <p class="mb-8 max-w-lg font-sans tracking-tight  sm:leading-snug leading-relaxed">Easily locate electric vehicle charging stations with our comprehensive and user-friendly &nbsp;map. &nbsp;Whether &nbsp;you're &nbsp;planning &nbsp;a &nbsp;trip &nbsp;or &nbsp;just need a quick charge, our service ensures you find the best and most convenient charging options. Start your journey with confidence and keep your EV powered up wherever you go.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center">
              <form method="get" action="/finder"><button class="inline-flex h-12 w-full items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-500 px-6 font-medium tracking-wide text-white shadow-md outline-none transition duration-200 hover:bg-green-400 focus:ring sm:w-auto">Find</button></form>
