                          <p class="text-gray-600">Trip Planner: Plan a route with charging stops based on your vehicle's range and the availability of charging stations along the way.</p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 px-4 mb-8">
                      <div class="bg-white p-8 shadow-md rounded-md">
                          <i class="fa-solid fa-charging-station text-4xl text-blue-500 mb-4"></i>
                          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Sustainability Tracking</h3>
                          <p class="text-gray-600">Eco-friendly Features: Information about the environmental impact of EV charging and how users are contributing to reducing carbon emissions.</p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
