      <!-- about -->

<div class="relative flex min-h-screen flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden bg-white py-6 sm:py-12" id="about">
  <div class="w-full items-center mx-auto max-w-screen-lg">
    <div class="group grid w-full grid-cols-2">
       <div>
        <div class="pr-12">
          <p class="peer mb-6 text-gray-400">
            At EV Plug Finder, our mission is to simplify the process of finding electric vehicle charging stations. We are dedicated to supporting the transition to sustainable transportation by providing a reliable and user-friendly platform for EV owners. Our goal is to make charging your electric vehicle as convenient and stress-free as possible, ensuring you can travel with confidence and ease.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6 text-gray-400">
            Founded by a group of EV enthusiasts, EV Plug Finder was born out of the need for a comprehensive and accessible resource for locating charging stations. We understand the challenges of maintaining an electric vehicle on the road and are committed to helping our users overcome these hurdles. With our extensive database and intuitive interface, we strive to be your trusted companion on every electric journey.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr-16 relative flex flex-col before:block before:absolute before:h-1/6 before:w-4 before:bg-blue-500 before:bottom-0 before:right-0 before:rounded-lg  before:transition-all group-hover:before:bg-orange-300 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-green-500 w-4/6 px-12 py-14 flex flex-col justify-center rounded-xl group-hover:bg-sky-600 transition-all ">
          <span class="block mb-10 font-bold group-hover:text-orange-300">HERE WE ARE</span>
          <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-3xl">
            "Charge Up and Go Green: Your EV Charging Guide"
          </h2>
        </div>
